description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 27, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 54, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and 1 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [54 Votes, Common]
